      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Landscaping and lawn care runs on reputation. Neighbors watch each other's yards — when a property suddenly looks immaculate, they want to know who did it. SocialProof helps you turn every happy customer into a visible endorsement on your website, so when their neighbor searches for a landscaper, you're the name that comes up with receipts.
